
The project uses <b>MERN</b> stack to generate images based on user's text prompt. The images are generated via <b>Stability AI</b>, which provides high-quality image generation services and a robust set of APIs for developers to build best-in-class image applications.

<h4>
    <b>🧑‍💻 Tech Stack: </b  MongoDB, Express, React.js, Node.js
</h4>

